  "body": "### Description\nAs a user, I want quick snap sync performance so that I can get my node up and running as quickly as possible. \n\n### Acceptance Criteria\n* Faster snap sync time than latest Besu\n\n**Actual behavior:** [What actually happens]\n* Do we need to verify the proof of work blocks? \n* Useless conversion from byte to RLP and back during sync \n* Sometimes we are stuck for some time during a snap sync \n\n**Frequency:** [What percentage of the time does it occur?]\nOften \n\n",
